articles.title: U-19 World Cup: Uday Saharan's India come up short against Australia in final - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Australia notch up a record total for the final in tournament history and Indian batters then struggle to lose by 79 runs at Benoni, South Africa. | Cricket
articles.content: Australia hadnt beaten India in their previous ten meetings at the U-19 level. They hadnt beaten India in two previous U-19 World Cup finals either. Now consign this information to the trash bin. Bec… [+4917 chars]
